sequenceDiagram
  participant User as Browser
  participant Rec as recommendation/routes.py
  participant TPL as templates/upload.html
  participant FS as /tmp CSV
  participant SK as sklearn KMeans

  User->>Rec: POST /upload (file)
  Rec->>FS: Save file
  Rec->>Rec: Read CSV, pivot(user_id x category)
  Rec->>SK: Fit KMeans(n=3)
  SK-->>Rec: labels
  Rec-->>User: Render upload.html (analytics + recs)

